<h1> On Lists </h1>

<p>
  There are moments when I feel very scattered while learning to program.
  When I am immersed in figuring out a particular coding challenge, I feel focused
  and the time flies by; however, when I emerge from the cloud of deep problem-solving
  thought, I often feel overwhelmed with the amount of things that I could be doing to
  advance my education. Always there are videos to watch, tutorials to run through,
  projects to build and continually work on, people to network with, articles to read, on and on.
</p>

<p>
  Enter <a href="http://www.trello.com" target="_blank">Trello</a>.
</p>

